container mx-auto w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center max-w-[384px] sm:max-w-[512px] lg:max-w-[900px]" data-translation-key="6f46a542-7fa8-4664-9ad6-634954935357"><h2 class="heading-light-800 w-full text-balance sm:heading-light-900 lg:heading-light-1000">Professional product photography without the time or expense</h2></div><div class="px-4 sm:px-16 md:px-32 lg:px-8 xl:px-10" data-translation-key="88a4f5ce-8468-4614-9052-af6fc277ea16"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center lg:grid-cols-2 mx-auto gap-4 sm:gap-6 max-w-sm sm:max-w-lg lg:max-w-[1200px]"><div class="relative"><div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-area-500 translate-x-0 translate-y-0" data-translation-key="72f2dd22-ad9b-4e2a-8651-2240fe5192c9" style="aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;"><video autoplay="" disablepictureinpicture="" loop="" playsinline="" class="h-full w-full object-cover"><source data-src="https://storyblok-cdn.photoroom.com/f/191576/x/4f9dc3ca36/remove-background-animation-v1_1.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video></div></div><div class="mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:pl-16"><div class="flex-1"><h2 class="heading-light-600 text-pretty sm:heading-light-700">Save time and money with AI background removal</h2></div><div class="body-600 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-8 text-content-secondary"><span class="[&amp;_*]:[word-break:break-word] [&amp;_*[id]]:scroll-mt-20 [&amp;_a[href]]:text-current [&amp;_a[href]]:underline [&amp;_a:not([href])]:!no-underline [&amp;_b]:font-500 [&amp;_strong]:font-500 [&amp;_code]:whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;_code]:break-all [&amp;_p_code]:inline-block [&amp;_p_code]:rounded-400 [&amp;_p_code]:bg-background-subdued [&amp;_p_code]:px-1.5 [&amp;_p_code]:align-middle [&amp;_p_code]:text-600 [&amp;_p_code]:font-500 [&amp;_p_code]:before:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_p_code]:after:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_blockquote]:[quotes:none] [&amp;_blockquote_p]:before:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_blockquote_p]:after:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_ul]:mt-3 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&am