r: transparent;"></div></div><div class="mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:-order-1 lg:pr-16"><div class="flex-1"><h2 class="heading-light-600 text-pretty sm:heading-light-700">Launch products faster by scaling background removal</h2></div><div class="body-600 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-8 text-content-secondary"><span class="[&amp;_*]:[word-break:break-word] [&amp;_*[id]]:scroll-mt-20 [&amp;_a[href]]:text-current [&amp;_a[href]]:underline [&amp;_a:not([href])]:!no-underline [&amp;_b]:font-500 [&amp;_strong]:font-500 [&amp;_code]:whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;_code]:break-all [&amp;_p_code]:inline-block [&amp;_p_code]:rounded-400 [&amp;_p_code]:bg-background-subdued [&amp;_p_code]:px-1.5 [&amp;_p_code]:align-middle [&amp;_p_code]:text-600 [&amp;_p_code]:font-500 [&amp;_p_code]:before:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_p_code]:after:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_blockquote]:[quotes:none] [&amp;_blockquote_p]:before:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_blockquote_p]:after:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_ul]:mt-3 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-4 [&amp;_.inline-next-element+*]:inline [&amp;_li_+_li]:pt-2 [&amp;&gt;div&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0"><div><p>Manually erasing backgrounds from hundreds of product images slows launch timelines and strains your team. Speed up workflows and handle large volumes of photo edits in minutes, from any device. Prepare for new e-commerce drops and update <a target="_self" href="https://www.photoroom.com/ai-product-photography/amazon">Amazon listings</a> with <a target="_self" href="https://www.photoroom.com/tools/batch-mode">Batch</a> or our <a target="_self" href="https://www.photoroom.com/api/marketplace-playground">API</a> to remove backgrounds across entire catalogs while maintaining consistent, high-quality visuals.</p></div></span><div><a class="relative inline-flex w-fit max-w-full appearance-none items-center justify-center overflow-hidden truncate text-center outline-none transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:misc-border-size-focus-ring disabled:pointe