ages with our full suite of <a target="_self" href="https://www.photoroom.com/tools">AI product photography tools</a>.</p></div></span><div><a class="relative inline-flex w-fit max-w-full appearance-none items-center justify-center overflow-hidden truncate text-center outline-none transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:misc-border-size-focus-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-not-allowed bg-background-default text-content-white-primary-inverted hover:bg-background-hover focus-visible:bg-background-hover focus-visible:ring-accent-alpha-5 active:bg-background-down rounded-500 disabled:opacity-30" aria-busy="false" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://app.photoroom.com/signup"><div class="relative flex max-w-full items-center justify-center content-to-edge-spacious-px-500 size-h-500"><span class="max-w-full truncate component-500">Get started for free</span></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col px-4 gap-i500 sm:px-6 md:px-8 pt-e500 pb-e700 bg-surface-default"><div class="mx-auto max-w-lg text-center lg:max-w-[600px]"><h3 class="heading-light-700 text-balance">Real results from brands and marketplaces using Photoroom</h3></div><div class="mx-auto max-w-[640px] px-4 md:px-6 lg:max-w-[1120px] lg:px-0 flex flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:gap-12 md:gap-x-20 lg:flex-nowrap"><div class="flex min-w-0 max-w-[256px] flex-col lg:flex-1"><strong class="heading-light-900 sm:heading-light-1100 text-content-accent">96%</strong><h4 class="heading-light-400 mt-2 text-pretty text-content-primary sm:heading-light-500 sm:mt-3">average boost in sales</h4></div><div class="flex min-w-0 max-w-[256px] flex-col lg:flex-1"><strong class="heading-light-900 sm:heading-light-1100 text-content-accent">93%</strong><h4 class="heading-light-400 mt-2 text-pretty text-content-primary sm:heading-light-500 sm:mt-3">reduction in photo editing costs</h4></div><div class="flex min-w-0 max-w-[256px] flex-col lg:flex-1"><strong class="heading-light-900 sm:heading-light-1100 text-content-accent">56%</strong><h4 class="heading-light-400 mt-2 text-pretty text-content-primary sm:heading-light-500 sm:mt-3">uplift in sell-through rate</h4></div><div class="flex min-w-0 max-w-[256px] flex-col lg:flex-1"><strong class="heading-light-900 sm:heading-light-1100 text-content-accent">99%</strong><h4 class="heading-light-400 mt-2 text-pretty text-content-primary sm:heading-light-500 sm:mt-3">visual branding compliance achieved </h4></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 xl:px-10 py-e500 gap-i500 items-stretch" data-translation-key="4cc04f1c-5d97-41d2-9531-301330beb891"><div class="@container mx-auto w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center max-w-[384px] sm:max-w-[512px] lg:max-w-[900px]" data-translation-key="4a2c3307-f66e-40fc-a2fa-0960134c529f"><h2 class="heading-light-800 w-full text-balance sm:heading-light-900 lg:heading-light-1000">How to remove a background from an image</h2></div><div class="mx-auto max-w-sm sm:max-w-lg lg:max-w-[1200px]"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[var(--step-cols)]" style="--step-cols: repeat(3, 1fr);"><div class="flex flex-col items-start rounded-area-500 bg-background-subdued p-6 sm:p-8 lg:flex-1" data-translation-key="f94ada5e-ed6f-462e-88fb-282cf9664ebb"><span class="inline-flex h-7 items-center justify-center px-2 component-semi-strong-500 rounded-200 bg-background-accent-subdued text-content-accent mb-3">Step 1</span><h3 class="body-semi-strong-700 text-content-primary">Choose a photo</h3><div class="body-600 mt-4 grow text-content-secondary"><span class="[&amp;&gt;div&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0"><div><p>Upload your JPEG or PNG product image; any size works. We'll take care of erasing the background for you. </p></div></span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col items-start rounded-area-500 bg-background-subdued p-6 sm:p-8 lg:flex-1" data-translation-key="7c2133ca-a246-4ae2-9692-8bce979f804d"><span class="inline-flex h-7 items-center justify-center px-2 component-semi-strong-500 rounded-200 bg-background-accent-subdued text-content-accent mb-3">Step 2</span><h3 class="body-semi-strong-700 text-content-primary">Let AI do the work</h3><div class="body-600 mt-4 grow text-content-secondary"><span class="[&amp;&gt;div&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0"><div><p>Photoroom removes the background. Keep it transparent or white, or pick your own color — it’s up to you.</p><blockquote><p></p></blockquote></div></span></div></div><div class="flex flex-col items-start rounded-area-500 bg-background-subdued p-6 sm:p-8 lg:flex-1" data-translation-key="65526628-85ad-4dd9-bf6a-8bbf6fcc6373"><span class="inline-flex h-7 items-center justify-center px-2 component-semi-strong-500 rounded-200 bg-background-accent-subdued text-content-accent mb-3">Step 3</span><h3 class="body-semi-strong-700 text-content-primary">Download your image</h3><div class="body-600 mt-4 grow text-content-secondary"><span class="[&amp;&gt;div&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0"><div><p>Download your photo in PNG, JPEG, or WEBP format, or save it to your Photoroom account to edit later.</p></div></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-translation-key="6395a334-4d22-4abf-aa2c-925b6b6415dc" class="flex flex-col items-center px-4 py-e500 gap-i500"><div class="@container mx-auto w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center max-w-[384px] sm:max-w-[512px] lg:max-w-[900px]" data-translation-key="6ce27e67-a1d3-428f-be95-9cbad39f5696"><h2 class="heading-light-800 w-full text-balance sm:heading-light-900 lg:heading-light-1000">All the AI product photography tools you need</h2><div class="body-600 w-full text-pretty text-content-secondary sm:body-700 @[512px]:max-w-[80%]"><span class="[&amp;_a]:text-current [&amp;_a]:underline [&amp;&gt;div&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0">Keep your brand looking sharp and consistent with Photoroom’s AI product photography tools.</span></div></div><div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[1200px] gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 l