;_p_code]:inline-block [&amp;_p_code]:rounded-400 [&amp;_p_code]:bg-background-subdued [&amp;_p_code]:px-1.5 [&amp;_p_code]:align-middle [&amp;_p_code]:text-600 [&amp;_p_code]:font-500 [&amp;_p_code]:before:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_p_code]:after:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_blockquote]:[quotes:none] [&amp;_blockquote_p]:before:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_blockquote_p]:after:[content:&#39;&#39;] [&amp;_ul]:mt-3 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-4 [&amp;_.inline-next-element+*]:inline [&amp;_li_+_li]:pt-2 [&amp;&gt;div&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0"><div><p>Photoroom is built specifically for e-commerce and brand visuals. Our AI background remover instantly erases backgrounds, leaving a transparent backdrop that you can replace with a studio or lifestyle setting, if necessary.</p></div></span></p></div></div></article><article><div class="group/faq-question flex cursor-pointer flex-row items-start justify-between gap-4 py-4 outline-none sm:py-6" role="button" aria-controls="faq-answer-:r4:"><h4 class="heading-light-400 pt-[5px] [word-break:break-word] sm:heading-light-500 sm:pt-[3px]">How does an AI background remover work?</h4><button type="button" class="relative inline-flex max-w-full appearance-none items-center justify-center overflow-hidden truncate text-center outline-none duration-200 focus-visible:misc-border-size-focus-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-not-allowed bg-background-subdued text-content-primary hover:bg-background-subdued-hover focus-visible:bg-background-subdued-hover focus-visible:ring-accent-alpha-5 active:bg-background-subdued-down rounded-500 disabled:opacity-30 h-8 w-8 shrink-0 rounded-full transition-all group-hover/faq-question:bg-background-subdued-hover" aria-busy="false"><div role="presentation" aria-hidden="true" class="flex items-center justify-center size-500"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-size-500" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M19 11H13V5C13 4.73478 12.8946 4.48043 12.70